f555", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2f362e79-479a-4670-ac1f-ef3f73b92c7c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d791318169b4fd86ada7cbdbcf0d46d7117986fbaf147f61b8e93046f871b29b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "23ec72e2-7dce-4dbd-a5c2-24eeea88bea5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a6ef83690e889ab9c1e50a0c5003d771c42bd21430232c4cb5cc803d4487c758", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "fd8725b3-522a-4afe-91e7-25fbebfb4532", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b450d1b0c57fc9f9303f9a6367d8a072d07af9da9e1b800368a4a874583eec66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 Definitions\n\nIn this agreement the following words have the meanings given to them below:\n\u201cconfidential information\u201d means any information disclosed by one party to the other party in connection with the purpose, which is of a confidential nature irrespective of whether it is marked as such.\u201cdisclosing party\u201d means the party to this agreement disclosing the confidential information.\u201cPwC firm\u201d means any entity or partnership within the worldwide network of PricewaterhouseCoopers firms and entities.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 452, "end_char_idx": 956, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "fd8725b3-522a-4afe-91e7-25fbebfb4532": {"__data__": {"id_": "fd8725b3-522a-4afe-91e7-25fbebfb4532", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2f362e79-479a-4670-ac1f-ef3f73b92c7c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d791318169b4fd86ada7cbdbcf0d46d7117986fbaf147f61b8e93046f871b29b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "73fb92cd-03c3-4118-9ced-f8bdbe49f555", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f1b8ebff6f59f1526e388020058d0971a49a216c203df489cd8d2b01ebc1dd8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "8c1d7245-0fe4-4176-a928-fbc94bf58fd2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "85a175167d78937678fa0687be1055b8280891140eab61dc44a21ad11d4c3528", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u201creceiving party\u201d means the party to this agreement to whom the confidential information is disclosed.\n\n2 Confidentiality\n\n2.1 The receiving party agrees:\n\n(a) to keep the disclosing party\u2019s confidential information, confidential;\n\n(b) not to use the disclosing party\u2019s confidential information except in connection with the purpose; and\n\n(c) not to disclose the disclosing party\u2019s confidential information to  anyone else.\n\n2.\n\n2 Each party agrees that it will keep the purpose and the existence of this agreement confidential.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 958, "end_char_idx": 1486, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8c1d7245-0fe4-4176-a928-fbc94bf58fd2": {"__data__": {"id_": "8c1d7245-0fe4-4176-a928-fbc94bf58fd2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2f362e79-479a-4670-ac1f-ef3f73b92c7c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d791318169b4fd86ada7cbdbcf0d46d7117986fbaf147f61b8e93046f871b29b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "fd8725b3-522a-4afe-91e7-25fbebfb4532", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b450d1b0c57fc9f9303f9a6367d8a072d07af9da9e1b800368a4a874583eec66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "17330f39-f0fa-4eb7-ba8e-85a5980225e9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "fbd30f7956e8190678f1aa3ce4ebaaaa950670820210aa12de52c7b33c9e3156", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2.3 This agreement will not apply to information which:\n\n(a) is publicly available; or\n\n(b) has been received from  someone else who owes no duty of confidence in relation to it;\n\n or\n\n(c) was already known by the receiving party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1488, "end_char_idx": 1718, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "17330f39-f0fa-4eb7-ba8e-85a5980225e9": {"__data__": {"id_": "17330f39-f0fa-4eb7-ba8e-85a5980225e9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2f362e79-479a-4670-ac1f-ef3f73b92c7c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d791318169b4fd86ada7cbdbcf0d46d7117986fbaf147f61b8e93046f871b29b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "8c1d7245-0fe4-4176-a928-fbc94bf58fd2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "85a175167d78937678fa0687be1055b8280891140eab61dc44a21ad11d4c3528", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a816971e-9ae0-4f08-b384-e2bd3bc9d322", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8e8471811d89ab6390cd27fb034d58f84ba45cf8cdb3ed3494014cf5b09b0d2d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2.4 Nothing in this agreement will prevent the receiving party from disclosing confidential information:\n\n(a) if the disclosing party has given its prior written consent; or\n\n(b) to its lawyers; or\n\n(c) if the disclosure is required by law, regulation or professional requirements; or (d) in the case of PwC, to other PwC firms or relevant subcontractors.\n\n2.5 The receiving party will ensure that anyone who receives confidential information under clause 2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1720, "end_char_idx": 2178, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a816971e-9ae0-4f08-b384-e2bd3bc9d322": {"__data__": {"id_": "a816971e-9ae0-4f08-b384-e2bd3bc9d322", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2f362e79-479a-4670-ac1f-ef3f73b92c7c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d791318169b4fd86ada7cbdbcf0d46d7117986fbaf147f61b8e93046f871b29b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "17330f39-f0fa-4eb7-ba8e-85a5980225e9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "fbd30f7956e8190678f1aa3ce4ebaaaa950670820210aa12de52c7b33c9e3156", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "73b9066a-9936-4287-bcd9-33dc661b28e4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8722750268fb750de1fdf4b07794ba1881481d04ec2cc8f8170048151d2e699d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "4 (b) is bound by confidentiality obligations before the confidential information is disclosed.\n\n2.\n\n6 Nothing in this agreement will restrict your ability to disclose PwC\u2019s advice concerning the tax (including social security) treatment or tax structure of any transaction regardless of any confidentiality markings on any communications.\n\n3 Term\n\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2180, "end_char_idx": 2531, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "73b9066a-9936-4287-bcd9-33dc661b28e4": {"__data__": {"id_": "73b9066a-9936-4287-bcd9-33dc661b28e4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2f362e79-479a-4670-ac1f-ef3f73b92c7c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d791318169b4fd86ada7cbdbcf0d46d7117986fbaf147f61b8e93046f871b29b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, 